{"tid":608640,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人嘅另一半好中意收埋自己","createTime":"2018-03-28T10:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T18:59:12.000Z","uid":142901,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dd71e568870ef8cefe0082e9c864c75bddd8ecb0","tid":608640,"uid":142901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T10:21:18.000Z","msg":"查實都同佢傾過好多次<br />\n亦都因為呢件事鬧咗好多次交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔係介意佢將自己嘅情感收埋<br />\n但係佢唔開心嘅原因通常都係誤會<br />\n<br />\n做醜人問佢做咩事呀佢又答無事<br />\n自己又偷偷地喺到唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都係想同佢搞清楚件事<br />\n唔想佢唔開心姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ed8135a29b3f1943c925defb244ebca34d037d","tid":608640,"uid":34768,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實都係唔想另一半擔心自己姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:鍾意收埋自己"},{"pid":"c5cfea60c9fe4211bf092e3fdebdcfc5245bae77","tid":608640,"uid":3505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"誤會到最後都係要灘出嚟講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cac2d0bf6c6de88a9830e4672f74b8981cb5947","tid":608640,"uid":142901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7ed8135a29b3f1943c925defb244ebca34d037d","tid":608640,"uid":34768,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實都係唔想另一半擔心自己姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:鍾意收埋自己"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T13:38:30.000Z","msg":"但你影響緊我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到你唔開心都想同你分擔<br />\n唔想淨係得你自己一個人食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395db52df6fe0c782606b21b25ba5b665b3cf295","tid":608640,"uid":142901,"